    <briefdescription>
<para>An istream that uses a BSON document as a buffer. </para>    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>While objects of this class do not own the underlying buffer, they do own the streambuf object associated with it.</para><para>By default, istream objects do not delete their streambuffers when they are destroyed, so this class allows one to create a stream without dealing with the underlying streambuf object. </para>    </detaileddescription>
